<plot>With a remarkable talent for getting things stuck to him, aspiring junior magician Ralphie Rauschenberg finds synchronicity in the most unlikely moment of his life. Annual career day seems headed for ruin, once Ralphie includes his chronically disappointed father in the latest of his misadventures. As their ambitions clash - magic handcuffs, a quarter-stealing bubblegum machine and fate have something else in store, giving them both a chance to redeem themselves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?184511</url></doc>
